description: The problem that this case study is dealing with predicts the location that a user is most likely to book for the first time. The accurate prediction helps to decrease the average time required to book by sharing more personalized recommendations and also in better forecasting of the demand. We use the browser’s session data as well as the user’s demographic information that is provided to us to create features that help in solving the problem.
